Always follow BPA_STANDARD.md and PROJECT_CONTEXT.md (see docs/).
Never change fixed ports (API 3000, Next.js 3100–3105).
Do not redesign UI; follow WowDash patterns.
Never overwrite existing code without merging; avoid deletions.
Prefer update-only patches and include exact apply steps.
Confirm affected files (touch points) before implementing changes.
Put all new .md files in docs/ (root only: README.md).

Prisma (production-like DB): never `migrate reset` or `db push` on this database; never edit applied migrations; new migration + review SQL + `migrate deploy`; run `node scripts/check-migration-integrity.js` before/after; on drift stop and plan (see docs/PRISMA_MIGRATION_NON_DESTRUCTIVE_POLICY.md).
